ximum 5 letter of intent signed by both the french and stanford coordinators indicating their commitment to work together on the proposed project 1 page maximum 2007 2012 stanford university 216 encina hall west stanford ca 94305 6045 phone 650.736 1321 fax 650.723 3010 ica information stanford edu drupal hit counter
